data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This home sits on a large corner lot with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 2 car garage with a custom large driveway suitable for a boat.  As you walk in, notice the vaulted ceilings with porcelain plank flooring throughout.  The great room is an open floor plan with the living room, dining room, and kitchen all seamlessly transitioned.  The Kitchen has self/soft closing doors and drawers, stainless steel appliances, and under-counter lighting.  The granite island contains a farm sink with a push-button disposal.  The master features a tray ceiling with crown molding and a custom walk-in closet.  The master-bathroom has dual sinks and a spectacular walk-in shower with custom tile work and glass walls.  The 8 ft sliding, pocket doors lead out to the pride and joy of this home.  Discover additional covered and screened in area with large decking space, outdoor fans and lighting to partake in the outdoor setting throughout the year.  Enjoy the custom outdoor kitchen with built-in grill & refrigerator and ice maker for a barbecue or refreshments.  Relax in the luxurious heated/PebbleTec pool.  For later entertainment, jump over to the beach for a nice fire.  This home is minutes away from beautiful beaches, shopping, dining, and fishing on Manasota Key and Boca Grande.  Have peace of mind knowing the home has a security system, whole home generator, and hurricane-rated shed.  It also has hurricane-rated windows, doors, and panels.  No flood insurance required and No HOA.  Whole Home Inspection, 4-Point, WDO, and Wind Mitigation inspections all completed by the current owner on 7/6.  The name on these inspections can be transferred over to the buyer and save the associated costs required by lenders and/or insurance companies.  Dimensions and lease restrictions to be verified by the buyer.
